_sText:
surf_exonic - Tier 6 Linear with 3 Bonuses


My favorite map as a kid was surf_exile, and I wanted to make a homage to Pyaniy ezhik's maps.

Exonic is heavily based off of surf_exile, hence the name, and uses a bigger, grander version of that map's detailing.

This map was designed for sv_maxvelocity 5000.

There's custom particles throughout the map, sadly the showcase video couldn't include them.
